item.title: CVE-2022-47557|2024-07-11T19:20:07.461Z -- ormazabal -- ekorccp
item.description: Vulnerability in ekorCCP and ekorRCI that could allow an attacker with access to the network where the device is located to decrypt the credentials of privileged users, and subsequently gain access to the system to perform malicious actions.
